[normal]10.1
[normal]&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
[normal]Janssen endorses the conclusions and recommendations outlined in the House of Commons Committee of Public Accounts report by the Department of Health, entitled 
[normal]The management of adult diabetes services in the NHS
[normal] (Seventeenth Report of Session 2012–13)
