[normal]&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
[normal]In summary, Janssen believe that d
[normal]iabetes care is too
[normal] often 
[normal]varied and inconsistent with unnecessary failings 
[normal]continuing to occur
[normal]. 
[normal]To prevent these instances from happening, better tr
[normal]aining and education for all healthcare professionals throughout the NHS should be introduced
